`,
    'docs/test-cases.md': `# Test Cases

## Primary Loop Test

| Test ID | Scenario | Source | Steps | Expected Result |
|---------|----------|--------|-------|-----------------|
| PL-001 | Happy path | requirements.md | Submit a repair description | See triage suggestion |

## Workflow Fallback Test

| Test ID | Scenario | Source | Steps | Expected Result |
|---------|----------|--------|-------|-----------------|
| WF-001 | Mock fallback | workflow-integration.md | Call /api/repairs/triage | Stable envelope returned |

